This directory contains helper scripts used to run the Broadband Platform
on Quakeworx. These osp_run.sh script is called by the gateway application
when the job starts. It will read the many environment variables set up
in the tapisjob.env file (which is written by the gateway and includes
all the options selected by the user).

The run.sh and run_debug.sh scripts are used to manually queue the
application on Expanse.
